text: Naresuan was ruler of Siam from 1590 to 1605. Naresuan may also refer to: * Naresuan University, a university in Thailand named after the king ** Naresuan University Hospital, a teaching hospital of the Faculty of Medicine Naresuan University * King Naresuan (film), a 2006 film based on the king's life * HTMS Naresuan, a Royal Thai Navy frigate
title: Naresuan (disambiguation)
